data.description: Peaceful Country Living awaits you tucked away with the scenic Leaf River running through the property. The original farmhouse was added on to with a large great room open to the kitchen, eating and dining area, brick fireplace surround by  windows to enjoy year around season views. Picture your horses, calves, sheep, chickens enjoying the pastures. The barn is set up for horses with stalls. A 45 x 23 outbuilding.  There is a garden area. Main floor primary bedroom with bath combined with laundry. Two bedrooms on main floor and two upstairs. Patio doors to the above ground pool. The miles of views are priceless!
